# ConvertType-Example

Run by C:
```
make
./main -i test.txt -o path
```

Run by python
```
python test.py
```

Input:
```
; Program Start
MOVJ VJ=40 100.001 0.000 10.000 0.0000 0.0000 0.0000
; First Toolpath Point
MOVL V=50 100.000 0.000 5.000 0.0000 0.0000 0.0000
; Plunge Move Starts
CALL LS_ON
MOVL V=8 100.000 0.000 0.000 0.0000 0.0000 0.0000
; Cutting Move Starts
MOVL V=17.3 0.000 0.000 0.000 0.0000 0.0000 0.0000
MOVL V=17 0.000 100.000 0.000 0.0000 0.0000 0.0000
MOVL V=17.6 200.000 100.000 0.000 0.0000 0.0000 0.0000
MOVL V=17 200.000 0.000 0.000 0.0000 0.0000 0.0000
MOVL V=17 100.000 0.000 0.000 0.0000 0.0000 0.0000
; Cutting Move Ends
CALL LS_OFF
MOVL V=50 100.000 0.000 10.000 0.0000 0.0000 0.0000
MOVL V=50 100.000 0.000 100.000 0.0000 0.0000 0.0000
; Last Toolpath Point
```
